priority 10000
snippet 'math(.*)math' "math" wr
`!p
import subprocess
code = match.group(1)
code = 'ToString[' + code + ', Tex Form]'
snip.rv = subprocess.check_output(['wolfram script', '-code', code])
`
endsnippet

